high_descs: Walk to the right towards the door and turn left to face the edge of the round wooden table.
Pick up the small tomato near the edge of the table.
Go to your left and turn right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato in the fridge beside another tomato, let it cool for a while, open the fridge, pick it up again and close the fridge.
Turn around, walk towards the counter top, turn left, walk to the wall and turn right to go to the trash can at the corner of the room.
Put the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the trash can at the corner of the room.

high_descs: Veer right to the other side of the table near the door.
Pick up the red apple on the table.
Turn left and walk, then veer right to the fridge.
Place the apple in the fridge to the right of the tomato. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk ahead, veering left to the garbage bin in the corner.
Place the apple in the garbage bin to the right of the cucumber.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in a garbage bin.

high_descs: Move to face the right side of the table near the gray bottle.
Pick the apple on the right up from the table.
Turn and cross the room and turn to the right to face the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the apple up and then shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the trash can to the left of the counter.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the trash can.
